YANG: A group of computer scientists called
the Clinton campaign last week to urge them

12:41.394 --> 12:47.433 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
to do this. Do they have any evidence or any
proof that something happened in these three

12:47.533 --> 12:49.302 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
states?

12:49.402 --> 12:53.039 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
SANGER: They don t seem to. I think the telling
