that s the critical thing, digitized as we

13:43.122 --> 13:49.862 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
get, John. Voting is one thing where you sort
of want to take a big step back and always

13:49.962 --> 13:55.435 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
have a paper backup. In Pennsylvania, that s
true only in a few parts of the state.

13:55.535 --> 14:00.173 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
YANG: Dr. Stein says she doesn t think this
would change the outcome and you have suggested

14:00.273 --> 14:04.210 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
