of that relief. However, I would say that

19:55.094 --> 20:01.100 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
the patience of Colombians has been really
tested out with this peace process and it

20:01.200 --> 20:06.439 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
hasn t been beneficial for anybody that this
peace deal has been going through so many

20:06.539 --> 20:08.074 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
