experiencing. If we can help equip young people

25:51.216 --> 25:55.354 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
in particular with healthy ways of dealing
with stress we can go a long way toward preventing

25:55.454 --> 25:57.289 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
substance abuse disorders.

25:57.389 --> 26:01.493 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
BRANGHAM: There are many people in the treatment
and the substance abuse world who are so cheered

26:01.593 --> 26:06.532 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
