There are others say it is too little, too

26:06.632 --> 26:13.272 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
late. I know Massachusetts senator Ed Markey
wrote that overdoses from the opioid epidemic

26:13.372 --> 26:19.845 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
