looked at alcohol, and it may surprise many

26:33.392 --> 26:39.398 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
people to recognize that alcohol leads to
the other substances in terms of cost and

26:39.498 --> 26:41.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
lives lost.

26:41.433 --> 26:45.370 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
So we dealt with a range of substances. If
you read the report carefully where you understand

26:45.471 --> 26:46.872 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
there is in fact a road map

26:46.972 --> 26:48.674 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
[0: 30: 00. 2]

26:48.774 --> 26:51.176 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
for how we should approach prevention and
how we should approach treatment, there is

26:51.276 --> 26:56.315 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
also attention to given to recovery because
what we have realized over time is that treatment

26:56.415 --> 27:01.620 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
