of relapses.

27:12.698 --> 27:19.371 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
My feeling is we have a number of concrete
steps in the report that communities can take

27:19.471 --> 27:25.511 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
