27:25.611 --> 27:30.282 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
defining the action doctors and nurses can
take but what policymakers and families and

27:30.382 --> 27:35.854 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
law enforcement and teachers and educators
need to take.

27:35.954 --> 27:40.058 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
This report has something for everyone. And
that s appropriate. Substance abuse disorders

27:40.158 --> 27:44.363 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
touch everyone. That s something I ve seen
firsthand and we all need to play a part in

27:44.463 --> 27:46.231 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
addressing addiction in America.

27:46.331 --> 27:49.601 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
BRANGHAM: Alright. Dr. Vivek Murthy, surgeon
general of the United States. Thank you very

27:49.701 --> 27:50.903 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

