29:03.208 --> 29:10.749 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Ages cuisine into a new career in his middle
ages, chronicling American food. His new book,

29:10.849 --> 29:15.320 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
"Ten Restaurants That Changed America," begins
