of saying we serve at 1:00, take it or leave

29:31.770 --> 29:33.505 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
it.

29:33.605 --> 29:37.409 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
SOLMAN: What fascinated me, as a money buff,
was how our restaurants track our economic

29:37.509 --> 29:39.411 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
growth.

29:39.511 --> 29:45.917 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
