29:47.819 --> 29:52.658 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
FREEDMAN: It coincides with an America of
railroads, of rapid expansion to the West,

29:52.758 --> 29:59.364 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
of industrialization and of increasing contact
with the rest of the world. It s not a place

29:59.464 --> 30:05.804 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
