or aristocrats. It s a place for enterprising

30:05.904 --> 30:06.805 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
people.

30:06.905 --> 30:08.073 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SOLMAN: But they are wealthy.

30:08.173 --> 30:09.941 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
