30:10.042 --> 30:15.213 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
SOLMAN: The new money wanted food that was
fancy French, with new world twists. Delmonico s

30:15.313 --> 30:16.748 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
