30:29.261 --> 30:31.563 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
SOLMAN: This was the place to meet and eat,well into the 20th century.

30:31.663 --> 30:34.332 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
UNIDENTIFIED MALE: We re going to Delmonico sfor supper, won t you join us?

