joined by the US surgeon general Dr. Vivek

01:01:00.524 --> 01:01:01.825 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
Murthy. Dr. , thank you very much for being
here.

01:01:01.925 --> 01:01:03.693 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
