01:01:03.793 --> 01:01:05.495 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
BRANGHAM: This is a pretty sobering report.
Millions of people suffering, very, very few

01:01:05.595 --> 01:01:06.062 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
