all this data, were you surprised by what

01:01:06.162 --> 01:01:07.964 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
you had found?

01:01:08.064 --> 01:01:09.966 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
MURTHY: Well, I had seen the problem up close
as a doctor practicing medicine. When I came

01:01:10.066 --> 01:01:11.835 align:left position:62.5%,start line:86.67% size:37.5%
