are the social supports and ongoing counseling

01:03:18.261 --> 01:03:20.030 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
that people need in order to reduce the amount
of relapses.

01:03:20.130 --> 01:03:21.865 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
My feeling is we have a number of concrete
steps in the report that communities can take

01:03:21.965 --> 01:03:23.700 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
and we, in fact, dedicate the entire last
