01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:25.035 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
defining the action doctors and nurses can
take but what policymakers and families and

01:03:25.135 --> 01:03:26.936 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
law enforcement and teachers and educators
need to take.

01:03:27.037 --> 01:03:28.772 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
This report has something for everyone. And
that s appropriate. Substance abuse disorders

01:03:28.872 --> 01:03:29.606 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
touch everyone. That s something I ve seen
firsthand and we all need to play a part in

01:03:29.706 --> 01:03:31.474 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
addressing addiction in America.

01:03:31.574 --> 01:03:31.908 align:left position:75%,start line:86.67% size:25%
BRANGHAM: Alright. Dr. Vivek Murthy, surgeon
general of the United States. Thank you very

01:03:32.008 --> 01:03:32.709 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

01:03:32.809 --> 01:03:34.644 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
